BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-Rcpp >= 0.12.4
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-RcppArmadillo 
Requires:         R-CRAN-Rcpp >= 0.12.4

%description
This program can be used to fit Gaussian linear mixed models (LMM).
Univariate and multivariate response models, multiple variance components,
as well as, certain correlation and covariance structures are supported.
In many occasions, the user can pick one of the several mixed model
fitting algorithms, which are explained further in the details section.
Some algorithms are specific to certain types of models (univariate or
multivariate, diagonal or non-diagonal residual, one or multiple variance
components, etc,...).

